Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.52,0:00:07.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TV动画「星刻的龙骑士」终于从4月起放松开始
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.90,0:00:06.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}翻译：Egoist.R  后期：小天   繁化：间谍
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.37,0:00:11.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了纪念在此献上特别企划
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.12,0:00:15.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庆祝星刻的龙骑士动画化 干杯！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.04,0:00:18.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好普通
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.94,0:00:22.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里请来了豪华的声优阵容召开派对
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.86,0:00:24.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.53,0:00:29.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这打扮是什么情况
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.96,0:00:30.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝色的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.48,0:00:34.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知为何竟然跳跃到了异世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.94,0:00:35.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更有
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.65,0:00:39.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 终于要去屠龙啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.53,0:00:43.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等着他们的是屠龙的任务？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.17,0:00:48.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有一只都不出来的时候嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.96,0:00:53.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇者高桥和小伙伴们的大冒险即将开始
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.74,0:00:59.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星刻的龙骑士 TV动画化纪念特集
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.84,0:01:02.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇者高桥 屠龙的试炼？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.01,0:01:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庆祝动画化 干杯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.62,0:01:11.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庆祝星刻的龙骑士动画化找开派对
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.10,0:01:18.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先来谈谈关于作品的看点
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.90,0:01:21.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看点是吗 看点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.38,0:01:25.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是那个吧 虽然很想说亚修的努力之类的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.64,0:01:28.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但重要的还是可爱的女主角的大量登场吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.77,0:01:32.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想广大粉丝肯定有着自己喜爱的角色
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.83,0:01:35.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想这会不会就是这部作品的看点
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.77,0:01:37.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.08,0:01:39.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说漏嘴了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.63,0:01:42.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪 这是为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.02,0:01:45.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是这样想的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.22,0:01:49.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家肯定有着自己喜欢的角色和她们的故事啊什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.57,0:01:52.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很好奇高桥喜欢的部分 比如说喜欢的片段啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.65,0:01:55.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所喜欢的片段吗 是的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.38,0:01:59.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就我来讲 有一集非常努力的去表演了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.15,0:02:01.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常希望大家能够收看的部分
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.36,0:02:06.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一话和第三话是相当的有看点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.83,0:02:12.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望大家能看到 在许多细节的小地方下了功夫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.16,0:02:15.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是从第一集开始就非常厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.96,0:02:20.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是战斗场面非常的吸引人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.24,0:02:23.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望大家能够看到 还有今后会有更多的龙出现
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.25,0:02:29.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和可爱的女孩子们一起 当然还有亚修
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.66,0:02:30.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.95,0:02:33.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然这里戳中笑点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.89,0:02:34.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.83,0:02:41.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来 派对仍在继续 让我们往下看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.21,0:02:46.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样 我准备了一个游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.53,0:02:56.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.47,0:03:02.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不是面朝着那边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.33,0:03:04.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从刚才开始就一直在看着他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.22,0:03:06.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在看着他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.41,0:03:09.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才笑出来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.63,0:03:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样子么？那么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.70,0:03:14.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害  干脆利落地就拆了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.97,0:03:18.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔细看看这个 难道没什么感想吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.77,0:03:21.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么想感慨的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.72,0:03:22.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 请加油
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.28,0:03:25.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我拜读一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.64,0:03:33.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再靠前来一点嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.57,0:03:37.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得人家穿的那么帅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.34,0:03:38.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么高桥君请读一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.41,0:03:40.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我读了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.29,0:03:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑暗之龙复活的时候到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.23,0:03:44.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 异界的勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.45,0:03:52.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是打扮是什么情况
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.94,0:03:53.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝色的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.05,0:03:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎来到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.72,0:03:59.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小伙伴们不都到齐了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.54,0:04:01.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇者高桥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.63,0:04:03.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说这里是哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.31,0:04:03.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是伊濑前辈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.94,0:04:05.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事情无所谓了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.49,0:04:08.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是僧侣佐仓
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.16,0:04:11.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是大家的僧侣佐仓
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.06,0:04:12.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是杂耍者伽美
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.89,0:04:15.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是杂耍者伽美 大家一起玩耍吧 伽美
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.79,0:04:17.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.18,0:04:18.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是说我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.88,0:04:21.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 你就是勇者高桥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.12,0:04:25.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您是伊濑前辈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.04,0:04:30.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不我不是伊濑 我是大魔导士茉莉也一世
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.26,0:04:38.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说你们好像是一部叫做星刻的龙骑士的作品的声优
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.38,0:04:40.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的本职工作
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.58,0:04:42.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就长话短说了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.35,0:04:45.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有事情要拜托你们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.61,0:04:55.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能否运用你们对于龙的知识助我屠龙一臂之力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.37,0:04:55.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在看什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.82,0:04:58.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然不会让你们白白付出
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.43,0:05:01.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果帮助了我的话 我就可以送你们回到原来的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.89,0:05:03.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我干 我当然干了 我也干
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.98,0:05:05.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.65,0:05:06.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇者高桥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.91,0:05:07.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.33,0:05:08.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.54,0:05:14.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.37,0:05:16.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐仓请你好好演嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.40,0:05:17.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有好好…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.29,0:05:19.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高桥君好好干哟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.63,0:05:25.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样勇者高桥和小伙伴们的屠龙冒险之旅开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.86,0:05:30.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去屠龙啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.96,0:05:34.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先想测试一下大家的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.25,0:05:37.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先是这里的门
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.76,0:05:41.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.90,0:05:42.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.27,0:05:49.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小龟？不是小龟 伽美
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.44,0:05:51.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伽美好像打不开
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.92,0:05:54.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打不开吗？那我来开吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.89,0:05:55.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.85,0:05:56.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打开了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.45,0:05:57.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GO~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.55,0:05:59.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GOGOGO
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.20,0:06:04.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.08,0:06:07.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.21,0:06:13.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来看看这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.42,0:06:14.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.75,0:06:18.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我家从古代开始代代相传的卷轴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.45,0:06:22.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.69,0:06:25.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去捕获龙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.16,0:06:28.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.41,0:06:31.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个该怎么读呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.36,0:06:33.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有土有龙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.00,0:06:34.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫古拉？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.36,0:06:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是僧侣佐仓
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.60,0:06:37.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.46,0:06:42.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 同样是龙 这次需要将土中之龙莫古拉捕获
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.33,0:06:45.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是我就试着讲打土龙再现了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.38,0:06:46.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.64,0:06:57.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用锤子敲击从洞中钻出的莫古拉并将其捕获
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.76,0:07:00.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每人30秒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.15,0:07:06.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3人合计达到100只以上即算任务成功
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.04,0:07:11.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先是勇者高桥的挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.69,0:07:15.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的那么 勇者高桥 你准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.55,0:07:16.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 没问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.17,0:07:19.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预备 开始
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.09,0:07:23.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.89,0:07:27.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.62,0:07:34.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有一个人都不出来的时候嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.62,0:07:36.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只土龙在偷懒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.74,0:07:37.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一只都不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.00,0:07:42.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家休息的时间都是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.16,0:07:49.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是打了很多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.94,0:07:54.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结束
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.65,0:07:56.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打了很多只呢 不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.41,0:07:57.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打了多少只呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.78,0:08:02.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇者高桥的记录 47只
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.02,0:08:04.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我试着努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.60,0:08:09.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来 僧侣佐仓 她是否能跟上这个速度呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.49,0:08:12.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来僧侣佐仓的挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.05,0:08:13.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放马过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.26,0:08:14.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.01,0:08:17.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好激烈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.81,0:08:23.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吓了我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.58,0:08:32.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.91,0:08:34.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.25,0:08:37.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像变难了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.22,0:08:43.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫古拉已经适应了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.10,0:08:51.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结束
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.69,0:08:53.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有股人臭味
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.57,0:09:00.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 僧侣佐仓的记录是 26只
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.92,0:09:03.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 伽美
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.28,0:09:06.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我变得超轻松了 我只要打13只就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.92,0:09:07.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.67,0:09:09.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,13只？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.99,0:09:13.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,100-73是多少？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.41,0:09:13.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,13？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.95,0:09:17.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,27 诶 不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.01,0:09:23.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伽美 伽美 伽美
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.20,0:09:24.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.09,0:09:28.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是13只 是27只 杂耍者伽美 拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.66,0:09:33.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一位 杂耍者伽美的挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.33,0:09:38.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伽美 不行啊 还没开始呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.81,0:09:40.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会打坏的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.37,0:09:42.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要打27只
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.42,0:09:43.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,27？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.36,0:09:46.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就可以通关啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.22,0:09:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.96,0:09:49.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伽美交给你了 嗯 交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.78,0:09:51.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 开始
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.74,0:09:53.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打到了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.16,0:09:55.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 打到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.14,0:10:00.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像挺用力的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.72,0:10:03.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面的人受到了相当大的伤害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.62,0:10:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有点远
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.03,0:10:06.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集中不了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.09,0:10:15.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都躲进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.96,0:10:20.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人还没有出来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.41,0:10:26.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小龟 那边有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.85,0:10:29.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.61,0:10:31.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伽美 不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.69,0:10:39.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 小龟伽美的成绩是17只
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.52,0:10:40.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过好像不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.77,0:10:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很努力了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.93,0:10:50.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 虽然很可惜 不过挑战失败
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.88,0:10:55.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太丢脸了 真的是太丢脸了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.69,0:10:56.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真那你们没办法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.94,0:10:57.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.90,0:11:01.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就让我拿出看家本领吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.58,0:11:03.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一世？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.42,0:11:06.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距离100只还有10只吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.36,0:11:09.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就让我用3秒来解决掉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.32,0:11:11.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3秒？ 3秒真的没问题吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.17,0:11:14.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在让你们见识一下我的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.78,0:11:17.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫古拉们哟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.96,0:11:21.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么？这个是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.28,0:11:24.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么你们只需要看着就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.30,0:11:28.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就来见识一下玛利亚一世的真本事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.60,0:11:31.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.08,0:11:33.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 都出来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.21,0:11:33.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.34,0:11:48.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是玛利亚一世的实力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.97,0:11:55.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.66,0:11:59.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.38,0:12:00.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.49,0:12:02.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.77,0:12:04.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.12,0:12:12.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于要屠龙去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.96,0:12:14.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很想这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.68,0:12:17.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是现在的力量还远远不足
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.43,0:12:23.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回更加严苛的试炼将像勇者高桥和小伙伴们袭来